### About
I'm a student of Software Engineering and Information Systems at [Faculty of Electrical Engineering and Computing](http://www.fer.unizg.hr/en/about/facts), University of Zagreb.  
Contact: [e-mail](mailto:jkeleme@gmail.com), [Facebook](https://www.facebook.com/jan.kelemen0).

### Projects
#### Coursework
* [Wild8](https://bitbucket.org/fgulan/anewhopeee) - Wild8 is a web page for a imaginary restaurant.
* [Compiler](https://github.com/jan-kelemen/p-p-j) - Compiler from simplified version of C to a FRISC assembler.
* [Zinoplex](https://github.com/jan-kelemen/diamond-dogs) - Bussiness biography tracker
